  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the tendency of plasma concentration and clearance
      of procalcitonin in the first 24 and 48 hours of management of patients with severe sepsis
      and septic shock with another marker of early prognosis represented by 48 hours delta sofa.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a cohort prospective observational study that will include adult patients admitted
      to a multidisciplinary ICU of a tertiary hospital.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
